VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT res\.cookie\s*\(|document\.cookie\s*=
WHEN EXPR MISSING:httpOnly\s*:\s*true|secure\s*:\s*true|sameSite|SameSite
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects cookie creation without essential security flags such as httpOnly, secure, and SameSite.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Missing Cookie Security Flags.
